{"tid":1937012,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"楊明燉湯舖所在工廈涉兩確診","createTime":"2020-03-21T15:20:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T17:56:23.000Z","uid":30873,"like":81,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6a2978e0115acd438611e12c3da0b319abc4fb61","tid":1937012,"uid":30873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T15:20:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2qhvwO3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2qhvwO3.png&h=23cc1d31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">長沙灣昌隆工業大廈一間公司，有二人中招，大廈與地鐵站相鄰。而藝人楊明的燉湯店亦在這工廈的地下。王瑋彤攝 (蘋果日報)</span><br />\n<br />\n另一個組群是長沙灣昌隆工業大廈一間公司，6人中有2人已確診，均沒有外遊紀錄。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">而藝人楊明的燉湯舖，也在長沙灣昌隆工業大廈。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n輸入個案開始衍生感染沒外遊的密切接觸者的情況，如第174號個案由瑞士返港後確診，導致與他一同飯敍而沒外遊紀錄的第162號及第222號個案也受感染。一名沒外遊紀錄的4歲女童，相信被她的父親（第114號）感染，她父親病發前曾到英國倫敦及格拉斯哥。沒外遊紀錄的第208號個案，曾接觸有外遊的第169號個案，不排除因而被傳染。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係好撚開心!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"378f3f5c4249580636eade6ca90c1a1d1635feb9","tid":1937012,"uid":117679,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T15:22:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啲員工會手走嚟走去⋯去其他分店⋯咁咪大檸樂。<br />\n<br />\n都係唔好去啦⋯"},{"pid":"4042fe7fda7af2b2d378c2bee7c862f005ed88e8","tid":1937012,"uid":315851,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T15:23:23.000Z","msg":"天網恢恢疏不漏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"797b4ad8edd7a531bbbc9a925086e9521bf6d92a","tid":1937012,"uid":30873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4042fe7fda7af2b2d378c2bee7c862f005ed88e8","tid":1937012,"uid":315851,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T15:23:23.000Z","msg":"天網恢恢疏不